      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNOOPING (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (30.56) at this track behind Tenacious Talker in a NG. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Makes plenty of appeal. SAMSON'S RIOT (6) hit the ground running to win over the 525m at Taree Super Track two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. STRUT (1) was out of the placings last time when sixth at this track (31.08) but scored four back at Rockhampton (29.73). Won at his only start from this box. Can figure in the finish. SWIFT BONNIE (5) must be included on latest effort.",
